{"tid":117783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普京一次撤掉16名將軍 同時任命緊急情況部副部長","createTime":"2017-02-12T13:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T17:10:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"323292468deb3694dda5eab0d07871d71f3ce95b","tid":117783,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:33:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>普京一次撤掉16名將軍 同時任命緊急情況部副部長</strong><br />\n2017-02-03 03:09:00<br />\n<br />\n【環球時報綜合報導】據俄羅斯媒體2日報導，俄羅斯總統普京簽署總統令，將緊急情況部、內務部和偵查委員會任職的16名將軍撤職。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據這份總統令，這16名將軍被撤銷所擔任的職務。目前尚不清楚此次人事變動的原因</span>。同一天，普京任命了緊急情況部兩位副部長。俄羅斯媒體對此沒有評論。<br />\n<br />\n據俄總統官方網站披露，16名軍官中有3名上將、3名中將和10名少將。這些被撤職的軍官此前分別在緊急情況部、內務部以及偵查委員會等強力部門任職。遭撤職的地區檢察長則曾在雅羅斯拉夫州任職。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2017-02/10051049.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fworld.huanqiu.com%2Fexclusive%2F2017-02%2F10051049.html&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuicp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b51599c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2017-02/10051049.html</a>"},{"pid":"913e102f913ba9f806a7976921840f85e613f86c","tid":117783,"uid":3794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"學史太林大清洗？"},{"pid":"386b3304fe9bc677bd9de32ab4f39bcdadd972e0","tid":117783,"uid":72277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"班友養唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362fdd9098d8d30259533a5b0713f5fe10dfcc22","tid":117783,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383e6ee2ba77fb9bb5fba07a5be4c929796259dc","tid":117783,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-